---

<section class="now" aria-labelledby="now-heading" id="now">
  <div class="wrap now-grid">
    <div class="now-head">
      <p class="eyebrow">Currently</p>
      <h2 id="now-heading">What I'm up&nbsp;to.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="now-body prose">
      <p class="lede">
        I'm a senior software engineer at <strong>Qualtrics</strong>, where I work on research tools with a focus on accessibility and thoughtful AI.
      </p>
      <p>
        Outside of work, I spend a lot of time in the mountains, usually trail running with an audiobook. I also paint, meditate, cook plant-based meals, and am learning the cello.
      </p>
      <p>
        Lately I've been looking at how modern AI tooling could help alternative proteins move faster. If that's your world, I'd love to connect.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .now {
    padding-block: var(--section-y);
    background: var(--paper);
  }

  .now-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    align-items: start;
  }

  @media (min-width: 860px) {
    .now-grid {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 14rem) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    }
  }

  .now-head h2 {
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 380;
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 96, "SOFT" 50;
  }

  .lede {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--fs-lead);
    font-weight: 380;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-6);
  }

  .now-body strong {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
</style>
